  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Bitcoin and The Power Law</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Bitcoin's growth follows the same mathematical pattern found in city scaling, biological metabolism, and network adoption. Not a prediction &mdash; an observation.</p>
  </div>

